<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08309</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROVIDING FOR PENSION AND HEALTH BENEFITS TO COMFORT WOMEN, APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Tasks the National Commission on the Role of Filipino Women (NCRFW) to determine the authenticity of the claims and identifies of comfort women with the assistance of the various accredited cause-oriented women’s group. 

Mandates the PVAO to provide Three Thousand Pesos (P3,000.00) monthly pension for comfort women and the Philhealth to provide free full medical insurance to comfort women as may be determine by the NCRFW.
</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “The Comfort Women Compensation and Benefit Act.”</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>NIETO, JOHN MARVIN &quot;YUL SERVO&quot; C.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-09-27</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Tambunting (000 2018-10-04)</td><td>2. Sy-Alvarado (000 2018-11-19)</td><tr><td>3. Malapitan (000 2018-11-27)</td><td>4. Sandoval (000 2018-11-29)</td><tr><td>5. Olivarez (000 2018-12-04)</td><td>6. Martinez (000 2018-12-05)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON WOMEN AND GENDER EQUALITY ON 2018-10-02</td></tr></table>